text: Michael 'Mick' O'Bryne (born 7 September 1988) is a Scottish footballer who played 'senior' for Dumbarton, Albion Rovers, Livingston, Airdrie and Stirling Albion. ==References== == External links == *Soccerbase Category:1988 births Category:Scottish footballers Category:Dumbarton F.C. players Category:Albion Rovers F.C. players Category:Livingston F.C. players Category:Airdrieonians F.C. players Category:Stirling Albion F.C. players Category:Scottish Football League players Category:Living people Category:Scottish Professional Football League players Category:Association football defenders
